verbose_text: In conclusion, our studies with Cry 1F resistant FAW, the first insect to have evolved resistance to a Bt plant in the field, allowed us to eliminate any potential prey-quality effects when examining the potential effect of Cry1F in a tri-trophic test with an important predator of FAW, C. maculata.
